/*!
    \page gltfEditor.html
    \title gltfEditor
    \ingroup tools

    \brief The gltfEditor is a tools that allows to preview and introspect
    glTF2 files rendered with the Kuesa Qt 3D engine.

    \image gltfEditor.jpg

    \section2 Features
    \list
    \li Introspect Entities
    \li Introspect Meshes
    \li Introspect Materials
    \li Introspect Textures
    \li Generate Normals
    \li Generate Tangents
    \li Preview Animations
    \li Preview different scenes
    \li Preview from the different cameras
    \li Compress glTF scene with Draco
    \li Export compressed glTF file with generated normals and tangents
    \endlist
